OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist and coastal low
OL,6,Fcloud will quickly burn away this
OL,7,Fmorning to leave a dry and sunny day.
OL,8,FFeeling hot with high levels of UV
OL,9,Fexpected.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSkies remaining largely clear
OL,12,Falthough some patchy cloud may move
OL,13,Finto the far east towards dawn.
OL,14,FRemaining warm with temperatures only
OL,15,Fslowly falling away.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,18,Ffor much of the region, although some
OL,19,Fcloud and a few spots of rain may move
OL,20,Finto Cumbria during the afternoon.
OL,21,FFeeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
