OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry and settled throughout Sunday and
OL,7,Fearly next week with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Remaining very warm although
OL,9,Fan easterly breeze will bring a little
OL,10,Frelief to the hot conditions.
